Package org.eclipse.cdt.core.dom.parser.c

Interface ICParserExtensionConfiguration

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractCParserExtensionConfiguration, ANSICParserExtensionConfiguration, GCCParserExtensionConfiguration
public interface ICParserExtensionConfiguration
C parser extension configuration interface.
Since:
4.0
See Also:
  • "http://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc/C-Extensions.html"
Restriction:
This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients. Clients can subclass AbstractCParserExtensionConfiguration instead.
Restriction:
This interface is not intended to be extended by clients.
